---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 1, 2025';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — HebrewEdu"
  description="Privacy Policy for the HebrewEdu app and website."
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="container legal-container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="display-lg mt-xs">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="lead mt-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <article class="legal-content">
        <section>
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>Learn Hebrew – Read & Speak developed by VIKTOR SOKOLIUK ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our Android educational app.</p>
          <p>By using the app, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>To enhance your experience, we may ask for certain personally identifiable information (such as progress data or preferences). This data is stored locally on your device and is not shared with other users.</p>
          <p>We also use Firebase, a third-party service provided by Google, to improve app functionality (such as crash reporting or remote configuration). Firebase may collect some anonymous usage data in accordance with <a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Firebase's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Our app is suitable for users of all ages, including children. However, we do not knowingly collect any personal data from children under 13. If we become aware that such data was collected unintentionally, we will delete it promptly.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. Data Deletion Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to request deletion of your personal data. To request data access, correction, or deletion, please contact us via email: <a href="mailto:vicsothemes@gmail.com">vicsothemes@gmail.com</a></p>
          <p>We will respond as soon as possible and act in accordance with applicable data protection laws.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any significant changes will be reflected in the app or posted through an updated document. We recommend reviewing this page occasionally to stay informed of updates.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Developer:</strong> VIKTOR SOKOLIUK</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:vicsothemes@gmail.com">vicsothemes@gmail.com</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>Thank you for using Learn Hebrew – Read & Speak!</p>
        </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
.legal-page { background: #f8f8f6; }

.legal-container {
  max-width: var(--w-narrow);
  padding-block: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
}

.legal-header {
  padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.legal-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }

.legal-content section h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
}

.legal-content p, .legal-content li {
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  line-height: 1.75;
}

.legal-content ul {
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.375rem;
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.legal-content strong { color: var(--ink-mid); }
.legal-content a { color: var(--brand); text-decoration: underline; }

/* Сброс глобального section { padding-block } */
.legal-content section { padding-block: 0; }
</style>
